            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="kimmelmannA" start="1266.831" end="x">Since the war we ourselves couldn't make it any more. But we were buying it from a factory and selling it to smaller businesses. But it was not permitted. We continued some time after the beginning of the war but then it didn't pay any more. It was too much of a risk. And so we gave it up. Shall I tell you all the details?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="1293.037" end="x">Yes.</span>
        </li>
