            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="kimmelmannA" start="1295.794" end="x">And so there was again a time that we pushed through as good as we could. In the summer it was said again that workers were needed for Germany. First of all the young people between eighteen and fifty.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="1320.668" end="x">Did you say fifty?</span>
        </li>
