            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Abraham Kimmelmann</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="kimmelmannA" start="11390.132" end="x">With the dead it was like this. There was no crematory in this <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>. But every Wednesday and Saturday there would come a truck and the dead were sent to <a class="placename" href="#vothC39" type="camp">Gross-Rosen</a> and there they were cremated.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
