            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="kimmelmannA" start="11415.149" end="x">And so the beating wasn't all. They wouldn't let us sleep. Every evening when we would return he would detain us in the eating hall, one couldn't go out to the toilet, we could go only in groups and only when one would take the responsibility for it, and every evening we were up until one, two o'clock at night, and at five o'clock we had to get up.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
